text: Dalila Abdulkadir in 2016 Dalila Abdulkadir Gosa (born June 27, 1998) is a Bahraini long-distance runner. She was scheduled to compete at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 5000 metres race but did not start the race. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Bahraini female long-distance runners Category:Olympic athletes of Bahrain Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics
